title: What Hi-Fi Sound and Vision Magazine UK January 2013
description: What Hi-Fi? Sound and Vision, the worlds no.1 home entertainment magazine now has a brand new look. Our comprehensive tests help you buy the best equipment for your cash and our advice sections give you step-by-step information on how to get even more from your music and Youll find more of everything in the new-look magazine from exclusive reviews and features to an enhanced Sound Advice section.
